					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1989677#post-2689708</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1989677/scp-2443#post-2689708</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 11 Nov 2016 17:29:16 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Heavenfall</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1341836</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I think maybe a line about adding people to the pile from outside would go a long way to dispel any notion of there being a lot of incest going on here. If the interviewed lady knows that the missing person is a grand-grand-nephew, that means they clearly know whose kid someone is.</p> <p>Heh, you could even say something about how the interviewed lady and the newly included person didn't get along for the first decade or so, but are all chummy now.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
